channel.title: AytonScape V8.0 (Not Mine)! 317 + Client!
channel.description:
Im only releasing this to this community Not mine i dont take any credits for the creation of this I took no participation in creating this i dont claim this is mine So please dont flame!!
It's Deltascape based, so if you wanna call me a leecher, go ahead. Since i got no players at my server, i decided to release. It's kinda barely coded, so please don't look at that. Also is my world PvP for still like 90% in it, you may need to add somethings.
Minigames: Castle Wars :D FunPk (Multi and 1 v 1) Fight Pits Pest Control Fight Caves Assault
Latest updates + Features:
Fixed godsword specials Delete world pvp (Like rs) - Can be added back when there are more players Fast Training + Elite Pk Pest control xp exchange Quest point system Added new interfaces Added anti starter stuff transfering Added sounds Added new dialogues [3-5 lined] Working black mask Made minigames (loads) better Added teleporting Better skills, full herblore New prayers (Mystic lore + Hawk eye) Cooking + Burning Global item drops Working ring of duelling, glory and games amulet New fight pits reward Report abuse system works Rune c bow works 13 quests New boss npcs Clan chat FunPK; Multi and 1 vs 1 without wildy levels. Castle wars Skill menus Statistics menu for players Blackmark system Real highscore page + stat signatures Full fight cave Fight pits Full wildy Full 1v1 Fully working prayer 100% 1 v 1 in Edgville All skills working Full special attacks Quests working (Bh)Skulls + Prayer Working lunars New prayers working Barrows degrading Crystal bow and shield degrading Working player following
Credits: Server: 90% Delta 5% To the community, for tuts etc. 5% To Ayton, for few edits
Client: 99% Bluur 1% to Ayton For Editing
